LIBRARIES REQUIRED FOR RUNNING ROBOT_AUTO_NAV PACKAGE IN UBUNTU:.................

Install Pygame:
sudp apt-get install python-pygame

Include Serial datagateway python file

Install Gmapping:
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-slam-gmapping

Install TF:
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-tf
rosrun tf tf_monitor //to monitor the transforms

Install map server:
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-map-server
rosrun map_server map_saver -f nameofmap //map_save
rosrun map_server map_server map_file.yaml   //to launch map file
rosservice call /static_map "{}"            //map service call

Install amcl package, move base & navigation packages
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-amcl
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-move-base
sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-navigation

....................................

